At Abdulellah Market, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our customers. This Privacy Policy outlines the information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have regarding your personal data. Please read this policy carefully to understand how we handle your information.

1. Information We Collect:

a. Personal Information:

Name
Contact information (email address, phone number, address)
Payment details
Billing and shipping information
b. Non-personal Information:

Cookies and similar technologies
Device information (IP address, browser type, device type)
2. How We Use Your Information:

a. Order Processing:

To fulfill and manage purchases and orders
To communicate with you regarding your order status
b. Customer Support:

To provide customer support and address inquiries
c. Marketing and Promotions:

To send promotional materials, discounts, and newsletters (with opt-out options)
d. Analytics:

To analyze website usage and improve our services
e. Legal Compliance:

To comply with applicable laws and regulations
3. Information Sharing:

a. Third-Party Service Providers:

We may share information with trusted third-party service providers to assist us in providing and improving our services.
b. Legal Requirements:

We may disclose personal information if required by law or in response to a legal request.
4. Your Choices:

a. Opt-out:

You can opt-out of receiving marketing communications.
b. Cookies:

You can control cookies through your browser settings.
5. Security:

a. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information.

6. Children's Privacy:

a. Our services are not directed at individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy:

a. We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices. Check our website for the latest version.

8. Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at [contact@abdulellahmarket.com].

By using Abdulellah Market's services, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

